<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL36">
<l>maḻaikkaṉṟu varaimu ṉēntu maintaṉē matura vāṟē</l>
<l>uḻaikkaṉṟē pōla nōkkamu ṭaiyavar valaiyuṭ paṭṭu</l>
<l>uḻaikkiṉṟēṟ keṉṉai nōkkā toḻivatē yuṉṉai yaṉṟē</l>
<l>aḻaikkiṉṟē ṉāti mūrtti yaraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O young Man who held ahead the mountain against the rains! O sweet River!</l>
<l>[Why do You] remain not seeing me, who am afflicted</l>
<l>being caught in the nets of [women] with fawn-like eyes?</l>
<l>Is it not You whom I have called out?</l>
<l rend="indent">O Primeval God! O [Lord] from the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
